OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774472757
OL,3,CThe plight of a woman caring for her
OL,4,Cex who's not aware he has a brain
OL,5,Cinjury
OL,7,FTheir insistence that they can cope is
OL,8,Foften taken at face value without
OL,9,Fconsidering their past history and
OL,10,Floved ones' concerns. This means that
OL,11,Fthey are left without the support they
OL,12,Fneed.
OL,14,FITV News has spent the last year
OL,15,Finvestigating this issue following the
OL,16,Fmurder of 24-year-old Christopher
OL,17,FLaskaris, an autistic man killed in
OL,18,Fhis own home in 2016, after he was not
OL,19,Fgiven a mental capacity assessment
OL,20,Fthat would have led to him having
OL,21,Fgreater support.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G22/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
